      "question": "The value of the exponent of $2$ in the prime factorization of $144$ is:",
      "answer": "(D)",
      "solution": {
        "steps": [
          "Perform prime factorization of $144$.",
          "$144 = 12 \\times 12 = (2^2 \\times 3) \\times (2^2 \\times 3) = 2^4 \\times 3^2$.",
          "The exponent of $2$ is $4$."
