      "question": "Given that $HCF(252, 594) = 18$, the $LCM(252, 594)$ is:",
      "answer": "(B)",
      "solution": {
        "steps": [
          "Use the formula $HCF \\times LCM = a \\times b$.",
          "$18 \\times LCM = 252 \\times 594$.",
          "$LCM = \\frac{252 \\times 594}{18} = 14 \\times 594 = 8316$."
